e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3a345c9fd9e7fbd2b37b50beedef691c567df28","tid":1471991,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"認同叫記者影（疑似）鬼大頭<br />\n引用其他post巴打嘅建議<br />\n好似之前tvb記者追問銅鑼灣鬼咁<br />\n一嚟可以俾人知有鬼 二嚟唔會對成場運動有負面影響<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲第25日</span></span><br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, 999唔通<br />\n無人落charge<br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6.疑似洗頭艇<br />\n（突發推上熱門）洗頭艇 被捕示威者被送到新屋嶺拘留中心<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446427</a><br />\n<br />\n香港811 back-up 影片 List<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3ezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ff62136e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLuJIeBxAm869d5llmCmHNJcF3agw79Hl8</a>"},{"pid":"714731b35554179a36a9585d9a3581e0aeb1bf4d","tid":1471991,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365ff8f5be3822efc30b870e51269a272b356b72","tid":1471991,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3549bd7e2fb28d7d46b5098d10fed53b5ebff0a0","tid":1471991,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"先唔講打<br />\n綁係一向嘅處理手法<br />\n你同我講係鬼起哄<br />\n你出過幾多次黎呀𡃁妹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"第一，一向既做法就代表岩？無普選一向都係政府既手法，代表岩？<br />\n第二，回應番我都係僅前線，幾乎次次出。<br />\n第三，上面講左兩個情況。<br />\n或者你講下點解綁？綁黎有咩用？解釋下比大家聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"on9類比<br />\n你都係收皮吧啦<br />\n尋日錯嘅係喺鏡頭面前